  <h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Process_Description"><span id="Process:_ITIL_Process_Evaluation">Process Description</span></span></h2>
  <p>A key change between ITIL V2 and ITIL V3 has been a new focus on continually improving services and processes. Service and <a class="mw-selflink selflink">Process Evaluations</a> are an essential element of "Continual Service Improvement (CSI)". </p>
  <p>To reflect the new structure of Service Strategy processes in <i><b>ITIL 2011</b></i> the interfaces of the process have been adapted. The process overview of <a href="/images/csitwo"  title="Itil-process-evaluation.jpg">ITIL Process Evaluation (.JPG)</a> shows the key information flows. </p>
  <p>&#160;</p>
